⍝ Expand.tc
⍝ ═════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO simple Boolean scalar or vector; Z nonscalar
      ⍝ inv: ¯1↓⍴Z ←→ ¯1↓⍴B
      ⍝ inv: ¯1↑⍴Z ←→ ⍴,LO   (expanded axis = length of LO)
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      LO ← 2∣|⎕RVAL 1 (,6) (,0 1 0 0 0)     ⍝ 6-element Boolean
      LO[1+5∣|⎕RVAL 0] ← 1                   ⍝ ensure at least one 1
      Z ← LO\B
      (¯1↓⍴Z) ≡ ¯1↓⍴B
1
      (¯1↑⍴Z) ≡ ⍴,LO
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴⍴B
1
